songs.title: Do you remember
songs.lyrics:
I still remember it
You still do not remember

You say you have too many things in your head
You say you have a lot of things in your hair

I remember very well
I remember perfectly
With details of how it happened

I know you for the most wonderful
One of the things that you have a space
In my rotten Heart, only 3 things can fit

I still remember it
You still do not remember

You say you have too many things in your head
You say you have a lot of things in your hair

I remember very well
I remember perfectly
With details of how it happened

I know you for the most wonderful
One of the things that you have a space
In my rotten Heart, only 3 things can fit

One of those things is you and will never stop being there
One of those is you
